1
00:00:02,220 --> 00:00:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna kill every one of you fuckers!</font>

2
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:08,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you dare hurt that lady!</font>

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look, Kaeko-san!</font>

4
00:00:16,410 --> 00:00:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mistress, stop staring at the 
back of his balls and flee!</font>

5
00:00:19,450 --> 00:00:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ogata! Stop laughing and grab him!</font>

6
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on here? 
Who are these people?</i></font>

7
00:00:25,940 --> 00:00:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't Yuusaku.</font>

8
00:00:28,680 --> 00:00:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell are you?</font>

9
00:00:37,800 --> 00:00:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flee, Norabo!</font>

10
00:00:40,630 --> 00:00:42,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll hold them off!</font>

11
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run!</font>

12
00:00:43,580 --> 00:00:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaeko-san!</font>

13
00:00:44,550 --> 00:00:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your clothes...</font>

14
00:00:45,510 --> 00:00:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just hurry!</font>

15
00:00:47,940 --> 00:00:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go! Go!</font>

16
00:00:49,990 --> 00:00:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

17
00:00:51,550 --> 00:00:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Sergeant Kikuta.</font>

18
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what's going on here.</font>

19
00:00:56,650 --> 00:00:59,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sergeant Kikuta was, in fact, doing his job.</font>

20
00:01:02,140 --> 00:01:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanazawa Yuusaku!</font>

21
00:01:04,030 --> 00:01:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the man from before...</font>

22
00:01:06,340 --> 00:01:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are your clothes?</font>

23
00:01:15,110 --> 00:01:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Sergeant Kikuta.</font>

24
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not him!</font>

25
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:33,290
<font size="40"><b>Golden Kamuy</b></font>

26
00:02:49,450 --> 00:02:54,290
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12" color="#62000d"><b>{\an3}Episode 58
Starting Gun of Resolve</b></font>

27
00:02:54,890 --> 00:02:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kikuta-san, who are those guys?</font>

28
00:02:57,650 --> 00:02:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No idea.</font>

29
00:02:58,950 --> 00:03:02,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's possible Commander Hanazawa had 
other people working for him besides me.</font>

30
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought this was your Plan B.</font>

31
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:10,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Plan B was to come up with a fake 
Commander Hanazawa and his wife.</font>

32
00:03:10,450 --> 00:03:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's also horrible.</font>

33
00:03:12,510 --> 00:03:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will they come after Kaeko-san?</font>

34
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:16,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To stop what Lady Hanazawa 
did from getting out.</font>

35
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need for that anymore.</font>

36
00:03:20,610 --> 00:03:22,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to marry you.</font>

37
00:03:26,810 --> 00:03:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm homeless, and my parents are gone.</font>

38
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have nothing.</font>

39
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My family has money!</font>

40
00:03:34,010 --> 00:03:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care!</font>

41
00:03:36,210 --> 00:03:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've lived in different 
worlds our whole lives.</font>

42
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:42,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you can get used to mine!</font>

43
00:03:42,530 --> 00:03:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can just live with me from now on.</font>

44
00:03:44,670 --> 00:03:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't have a home, 
where are you going to live from now on?</font>

45
00:03:48,550 --> 00:03:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll join the army, maybe.</font>

46
00:03:50,530 --> 00:03:53,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm told they have white rice, at least.</font>

47
00:03:55,410 --> 00:03:59,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mistress, marriage is something 
that binds two houses together.</font>

48
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your family will never allow it.</font>

49
00:04:02,210 --> 00:04:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You only care so much about how 
much a man looks because you</font>

50
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">want to get back at all your schoolmates 
who got married before you, right?</font>

51
00:04:09,740 --> 00:04:12,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The idea your school has that girls 
who don't get married are leftovers</font>

52
00:04:12,970 --> 00:04:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is bullshit.</font>

53
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to have a man next 
to you to restore your self-respect.</font>

54
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're capable of proving 
your worth on your own.</font>

55
00:04:25,610 --> 00:04:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Hamako.</font>

56
00:04:29,650 --> 00:04:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for deceiving you.</font>

57
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to you, I was able to get a brief 
glimpse of a wonderful other world.</font>

58
00:04:37,370 --> 00:04:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Farewell.</font>

59
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:41,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please become a handsome soldier.</font>

60
00:04:42,210 --> 00:04:49,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kaneko Kaeko would go on to become a 
financial titan known as the Empress.</i></font>

61
00:04:49,030 --> 00:04:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But what's not as well known is that 
during the Russo-Japanese war,</i></font>

62
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she spared no expense to aid war 
widows and care for the wounded.</i></font>

63
00:05:11,370 --> 00:05:13,880
<font face="Times New Roman" size="25" color="#5a6461"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"></font></b><font color="#9d9284"><font size="20">{\an5}Choya Shimbun</font></font></font>

64
00:05:13,380 --> 00:05:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow...</font>

65
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're crazy, getting shot 
protecting a guy like me!</font>

66
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who got you 
involved after all.</font>

67
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. And anyway...</font>

68
00:05:27,020 --> 00:05:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got a first-class seat to hell.</font>

69
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget about me.</font>

70
00:05:31,530 --> 00:05:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And all about Hanazawa Yuusaku, too.</font>

71
00:05:34,780 --> 00:05:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What you said about joining the army...</font>

72
00:05:37,230 --> 00:05:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not serious, right?</font>

73
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for everything.</font>

74
00:05:40,650 --> 00:05:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me back that cap, please.</font>

75
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hanazawa Yuusaku told me that 
this was your brother's,</font>

76
00:05:46,150 --> 00:05:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that he died during 
the Sino-Japanese war.</font>

77
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you said you had a 
first-class seat to hell...</font>

78
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you blame yourself for 
your brother's death?</font>

79
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who told him to join the army.</font>

80
00:05:57,540 --> 00:06:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our family was poor. I told him he 
could at least make sure he was fed.</font>

81
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More people died of disease 
than bullets during that war.</font>

82
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I hadn't talked him into joining, 
he wouldn't have suffered and died.</font>

83
00:06:10,490 --> 00:06:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I basically murdered him.</font>

84
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:18,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true that you're the reason 
I thought of joining the army.</font>

85
00:06:19,570 --> 00:06:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in the end, it's my call to make.</font>

86
00:06:21,930 --> 00:06:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what happens, 
I'll never be angry with you.</font>

87
00:06:25,020 --> 00:06:28,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you forgive 
yourself, and move on?</font>

88
00:06:30,330 --> 00:06:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it won't be that easy 
for anybody to kill me.</font>

89
00:06:32,930 --> 00:06:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm immortal!</font>

90
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep the cap.</font>

91
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:44,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell Hanazawa Yuusaku about the lady!</font>

92
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has the right to choose!</font>

93
00:06:48,490 --> 00:06:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a problem for the whole army now.</font>

94
00:06:52,970 --> 00:06:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'd get kicked out, too.</font>

95
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget this whole thing.</font>

96
00:06:58,170 --> 00:07:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we see each other in the army,</font>

97
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:02,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">let's pretend we've never met.</font>

98
00:07:03,860 --> 00:07:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you around, Norabo.</font>

99
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:12,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sergeant Kikuta, I'm sending you 
to the 7th Division.</font>

100
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come up with your own 
reason for the transfer.</font>

101
00:07:15,780 --> 00:07:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get close to Lieutenant Tsurumi and 
report to the central government.</font>

102
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:22,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch him and make sure he 
doesn't get out of control.</font>

103
00:07:23,930 --> 00:07:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's this?</font>

104
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll be doing the same thing.</font>

105
00:07:27,370 --> 00:07:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But to make sure you're both not caught 
at once, I want you to act separately.</font>

106
00:07:31,650 --> 00:07:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just don't get in each other's way.</font>

107
00:07:33,970 --> 00:07:36,470
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>1904: Hill 203</b></font>

108
00:07:43,010 --> 00:07:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuusaku-dono! Yuusaku-dono! Yuusaku-dono!</font>

109
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:58,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So Norabo was a hero of 
the Russo-Japanese war.</i></font>

110
00:07:58,830 --> 00:08:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I'm the one who got 
him to join the army.</i></font>

111
00:08:02,450 --> 00:08:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I guess that's a win for me.</i></font>

112
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time we meet, I'll have 
to fight Kikuta-san for real.</i></font>

113
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this?</font>

114
00:08:12,220 --> 00:08:12,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ko.</font>

115
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait... This can't be...</font>

116
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got it.</font>

117
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:29,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the location of the gold?</font>

118
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At last...</font>

119
00:08:31,150 --> 00:08:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At last, the war for 
the gold will end, huh?</font>

120
00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no.</font>

121
00:08:37,670 --> 00:08:39,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's only just beginning.</font>

122
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what this is, right, 
Warrant Officer Kikuta?</font>

123
00:08:54,930 --> 00:08:56,930
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>Sapporo Nakajima Amusement Park</b></font>

124
00:08:59,650 --> 00:09:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The dead drop.</i></font>

125
00:09:01,930 --> 00:09:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An old method used by spies.</i></font>

126
00:09:05,220 --> 00:09:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A technique for handing something 
over without physically meeting.</i></font>

127
00:09:11,420 --> 00:09:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I found a cigarette.</font>

128
00:09:14,570 --> 00:09:16,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait! You there!</font>

129
00:09:22,420 --> 00:09:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told them somebody would 
pick up a cigarette.</font>

130
00:09:26,290 --> 00:09:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got careless in my absence.</font>

131
00:09:31,620 --> 00:09:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Private Usami did well.</font>

132
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The copied skins... and this...</font>

133
00:09:39,130 --> 00:09:43,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're finished, Lieutenant Tsurumi.</font>

134
00:09:44,070 --> 00:09:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be killed.</font>

135
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what you want to say.</font>

136
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they can't be sure you're alive,</font>

137
00:09:52,650 --> 00:09:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the central government will come to 
put a stop to me for good, right?</font>

138
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The gunshot that killed 
Warrant Officer Kikuta</font>

139
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is a sign that we have just 
destroyed our own line of retreat,</font>

140
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and have no choice but 
to capture the gold!</font>

141
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:13,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the starting gun of our resolve!</font>

142
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not talking about 
the central government.</font>

143
00:10:17,340 --> 00:10:20,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be Norabo that takes you down.</font>

144
00:10:20,470 --> 00:10:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Norabo?</font>

145
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got a first-class seat to hell.</font>

146
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll make sure 
there's room next to me.</font>

147
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lieutenant Tsurumi only sits next to me.</font>

148
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sugimoto.</font>

149
00:10:36,450 --> 00:10:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think we've got it.</font>

150
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell all our forces scattered 
around the island!</font>

151
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do whatever it takes to get 
here as soon as possible!</font>

152
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Load your warhorses with weapons and ammo!</font>

153
00:10:48,460 --> 00:10:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And come as fast as you can without rest!</font>

154
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:55,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The gold's here?</font>

155
00:10:55,340 --> 00:10:57,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do I read this?</font>

156
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This line.</font>

157
00:10:58,940 --> 00:11:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one that crosses the others.</font>

158
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you see it?</font>

159
00:11:07,550 --> 00:11:08,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fort Goryoukaku!</font>

160
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There, of all places.</font>

161
00:11:12,870 --> 00:11:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This has gotten interesting, huh Gamushin?</font>

162
00:11:16,110 --> 00:11:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The fact that the code could be 
cracked without all the skins...</i></font>

163
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Resulted in both Hijikata 
Toshizou and Lieutenant Tsurumi</i></font>

164
00:11:26,540 --> 00:11:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>solving it at almost the same time!</i></font>

165
00:11:33,130 --> 00:11:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait a second.</font>

166
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that the copy of your skin?</font>

167
00:11:38,570 --> 00:11:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It fits here perfectly.</font>

168
00:11:45,410 --> 00:11:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We didn't need it at all!</font>

169
00:11:47,650 --> 00:11:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hakodate...</i></font>

170
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:55,020
<font size="40"><b><font color="#f5f5f1">Golden Kamuy</font></b></font>

171
00:11:55,020 --> 00:12:00,400
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#010101">Mt. Hakodate</font></font></b></font>

172
00:11:55,020 --> 00:12:00,400
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#010101">Hakodate Station</font></font></b></font>

173
00:11:55,020 --> 00:12:00,400
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#010101">Fort Goryoukaku</font></font></b></font>

174
00:11:55,740 --> 00:11:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hakodate!</i></font>

175
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The oldest port in Hokkaido</i></font>

176
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that was opened to the outside world 
and a center of international trade.</i></font>

177
00:12:04,590 --> 00:12:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There are many consulates 
and churches here.</i></font>

178
00:12:09,810 --> 00:12:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really shaped like a star?</font>

179
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:14,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so big I can't even imagine.</font>

180
00:12:14,650 --> 00:12:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How big is it?</font>

181
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">1.8 kilometers, if you 
go along the outer moat.</font>

182
00:12:22,310 --> 00:12:27,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Approximately 550 meters 
from this side to this one.</font>

183
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:30,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is Goryoukaku, anyway?</font>

184
00:12:30,940 --> 00:12:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The remains of a castle.</font>

185
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Hakodate Magistrate, a government 
building run by the Edo Shogunate,</font>

186
00:12:36,410 --> 00:12:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was located in its center.</font>

187
00:12:39,370 --> 00:12:42,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Protecting Hokkaido from 
Russian expansionism,</font>

188
00:12:42,060 --> 00:12:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">diplomacy with Europe and America...</font>

189
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was created to be the 
political center of Ezo.</font>

190
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:50,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The outer walls are all that's left.</font>

191
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the last place we soldiers of the 
Shogunate fought the revolutionary army.</font>

192
00:12:56,850 --> 00:12:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our last great stage.</font>

193
00:12:59,430 --> 00:13:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's said that Hijikata 
Toshizou died at Hakodate.</font>

194
00:13:04,410 --> 00:13:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"All that remains of soldiers' dreams."</font>

195
00:13:07,250 --> 00:13:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our dream ends at Goryoukaku.</font>

196
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:15,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And a new dream will 
begin at Goryoukaku, too.</font>

197
00:13:15,890 --> 00:13:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The army used it as a training 
ground until 1897, I heard.</font>

198
00:13:21,020 --> 00:13:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now it's empty.</font>

199
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are no homes near this place, 
so normally nobody comes here.</font>

200
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they hid it in a place where the 
army once had a training ground?</font>

201
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess they thought the army'd 
never bother to look there.</font>

202
00:13:33,060 --> 00:13:34,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a bold choice.</font>

203
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did Nopperabo bring the gold from?</font>

204
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to what Botaro the 
Pirate heard from the old Ainu,</font>

205
00:13:43,370 --> 00:13:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it was seven kilometers to the southwest.</font>

206
00:13:46,810 --> 00:13:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Russian consulate on Mt. Hakodate.</font>

207
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kimuspu, this is where the gold is, right?</font>

208
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was here when the gold was 
carried into this building.</font>

209
00:14:00,020 --> 00:14:02,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll go around the back and go inside.</font>

210
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Russian ambassador who 
lived here was a greedy man,</font>

211
00:14:06,650 --> 00:14:09,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who tried to work with 
members of their military</font>

212
00:14:09,660 --> 00:14:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to sell us Ainu weapons and a warship.</font>

213
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the ship got into an accident.</font>

214
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ambassador, his family, 
and the officers were all aboard,</font>

215
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they all sank with it.</font>

216
00:14:20,990 --> 00:14:23,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since relations with Japan 
were getting worse,</font>

217
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">no new ambassador ever came.</font>

218
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place has been locked up ever since.</font>

219
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:30,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way.</font>

220
00:14:30,770 --> 00:14:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wall in the library in the back.</font>

221
00:14:34,450 --> 00:14:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We put this wall up after he died.</font>

222
00:14:40,730 --> 00:14:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone but me who went down 
into this basement is now dead.</font>

223
00:14:45,650 --> 00:14:47,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone's outside!</font>

224
00:14:59,770 --> 00:15:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otonoshin will have to die.</font>

225
00:15:10,260 --> 00:15:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that about?</font>

226
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever it was, 
this place isn't safe anymore.</font>

227
00:15:19,230 --> 00:15:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get the light closer.</font>

228
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wenkamuy killed them all.</font>

229
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

230
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kimuspu.</font>

231
00:15:31,090 --> 00:15:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on here?</font>

232
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When cracking the code,</font>

233
00:15:37,090 --> 00:15:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without Botaro the Pirate's 
hint about Hakodate,</font>

234
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we wouldn't have thought of this 
place's star shape so soon.</font>

235
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:47,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no time to waste.</font>

236
00:15:47,470 --> 00:15:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll hurry and find it!</font>

237
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Old Man Nagakura, calm down.</font>

238
00:15:53,540 --> 00:15:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got here ahead of Lieutenant Tsurumi
and his men, thanks to Botaro.</font>

239
00:15:57,570 --> 00:16:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might take them days to crack the code.</font>

240
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

241
00:16:03,770 --> 00:16:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These guys...</font>

242
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get down.</font>

243
00:16:21,820 --> 00:16:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any more soldiers' footsteps?</font>

244
00:16:24,910 --> 00:16:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody close.</font>

245
00:16:27,950 --> 00:16:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're carrying a telegram.</font>

246
00:16:30,450 --> 00:16:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's from... Lieutenant Tsurumi!</font>

247
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It came from Sapporo! One hour ago!</font>

248
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Head to Goryoukaku, immediately!"</font>

249
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no...</font>

250
00:16:41,140 --> 00:16:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They solved the code, too...</font>

251
00:16:44,140 --> 00:16:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long before they're here?</font>

252
00:16:46,950 --> 00:16:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are two trains that travel 
between Sapporo and Hakodate each day.</font>

253
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:51,400
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#000000">Sapporo</font></b></font>

254
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:51,400
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#000000">Otaru</font></b></font>

255
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:51,400
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font color="#000000">Hakodate</font></b></font>

256
00:16:51,690 --> 00:16:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Assuming he leaves in the morning, 
that should give us a full day.</font>

257
00:16:56,330 --> 00:16:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And a horse would take even longer.</font>

258
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see!</font>

259
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Lieutenant Tsurumi might 
hijack a waiting train.</font>

260
00:17:06,090 --> 00:17:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'd get him here in 12 hours.</font>

261
00:17:10,130 --> 00:17:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No time to waste! Get digging!</font>

262
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down, Shiraishi! 
I'm pretty sure it's not there!</font>

263
00:17:16,430 --> 00:17:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then where is the gold?</font>

264
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The code didn't have any hints?</font>

265
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:23,450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font color="#d5c444"><font size="30">Gold</font></font></b></font>

266
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There wasn't the character 
for "gold" anyway?</font>

267
00:17:23,490 --> 00:17:25,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to dig it up and run!</font>

268
00:17:25,770 --> 00:17:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are several buildings inside.</font>

269
00:17:29,690 --> 00:17:34,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That old storehouse 
predates the Hakodate war.</font>

270
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the smaller buildings 
the Army put up...</font>

271
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Ainu would've known about them, too.</font>

272
00:17:42,570 --> 00:17:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's likely they hid them under 
the floors of one of them.</font>

273
00:17:46,660 --> 00:17:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should search there first.</font>

274
00:17:50,210 --> 00:17:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't say you're wrong...</font>

275
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But wouldn't it be faster to toss 
it all into one of the moats?</font>

276
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:59,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gold dust won't rust 
underwater, after all.</font>

277
00:17:59,150 --> 00:18:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then they may have hid it in a well.</font>

278
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not here!</font>

279
00:18:07,410 --> 00:18:08,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down!</font>

280
00:18:08,850 --> 00:18:11,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, where's Kadokura and Kirawus?</font>

281
00:18:11,420 --> 00:18:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Kantarou.</font>

282
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to find them.</font>

283
00:18:14,870 --> 00:18:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We split up at the station. 
They're getting a cart for us.</font>

284
00:18:18,530 --> 00:18:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got another problem.</font>

285
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Assuming we find it, 
how far can we get with it?</font>

286
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:29,500
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#020302">Mt. Hakodate</font></b></font>

287
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aca and his friends must've made 
that seven-kilometer journey many times.</font>

288
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How much gold can a cart carry?</font>

289
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we assume a horse can pull 
twice its weight, 800 kilograms.</font>

290
00:18:38,730 --> 00:18:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Assume one bag weighs 60 kilograms. 
That's 13 bags at most.</font>

291
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No problem, then, assuming 
they can bring 90 carts.</font>

292
00:18:47,580 --> 00:18:48,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not happening!</font>

293
00:18:48,850 --> 00:18:50,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what's that square on your head?</font>

294
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:53,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, geezer, what was the plan here?</font>

295
00:18:53,770 --> 00:18:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you even have one?</font>

296
00:18:56,220 --> 00:19:02,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody expected we'd have twelve 
hours to get the gold out, obviously!</font>

297
00:19:04,410 --> 00:19:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even Wilk didn't assume two sides would 
crack the code at almost the same time.</font>

298
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:14,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're screwed, then.</font>

299
00:19:14,450 --> 00:19:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have to fight.</font>

300
00:19:15,860 --> 00:19:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can hole ourselves up here, and fight.</font>

301
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

302
00:19:20,010 --> 00:19:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fight the whole 7th 
Division? By ourselves?</font>

303
00:19:22,760 --> 00:19:24,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've arranged things.</font>

304
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though I didn't expect things 
to be cutting it this close.</font>

305
00:19:30,270 --> 00:19:33,020
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>14 Hours Earlier</b></font>

306
00:19:33,380 --> 00:19:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We came on this ship to follow Asirpa.</font>

307
00:19:36,060 --> 00:19:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Friends are waiting in Otaru.</font>

308
00:19:38,130 --> 00:19:39,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many?</font>

309
00:19:39,530 --> 00:19:41,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One hundred twenty.</font>

310
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weapons, too.</font>

311
00:19:42,840 --> 00:19:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to bring your comrades 
from Otaru via the afternoon train.</font>

312
00:19:55,410 --> 00:19:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm shocked Sofia decided to 
work with Hijikata Toshizou.</font>

313
00:19:59,770 --> 00:20:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've been fighting for the far 
east Russian minorities, right?</font>

314
00:20:04,220 --> 00:20:06,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would they change their minds that easily?</font>

315
00:20:06,100 --> 00:20:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. Kiroranke 
gave up his life for that.</font>

316
00:20:10,030 --> 00:20:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we trust them?</font>

317
00:20:11,860 --> 00:20:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They may steal all the gold.</font>

318
00:20:14,730 --> 00:20:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that happens, we deal with it.</font>

319
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have little hope of 
winning without them.</font>

320
00:20:20,740 --> 00:20:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Lieutenant Tsurumi gets the 
gold, we get nothing.</font>

321
00:20:25,730 --> 00:20:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think we can trust Sofia.</font>

322
00:20:28,930 --> 00:20:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We will migrate to this land, set 
down roots, and gather strength.</font>

323
00:20:36,020 --> 00:20:43,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is the multicultural Hokkaido 
that Comrade Wilk wanted.</font>

324
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And someday this will be our base 
of operations against Russia.</font>

325
00:20:50,620 --> 00:20:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That is the Far East Federation 
that Comrade Yulbars wanted.</font>

326
00:20:55,920 --> 00:21:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I won't deny either Wilk 
nor Yulbars their dream.</font>

327
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That is my decision. 
Now decide if you'll follow me.</font>

328
00:21:14,620 --> 00:21:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What country are these gaijin from?</font>

329
00:21:18,230 --> 00:21:24,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The going is easy, 
but the way back is scary...</i></font>

330
00:21:24,840 --> 00:21:26,840
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>Sapporo Rail Yard</b></font>

331
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We thank you for your cooperation.</font>

332
00:21:41,270 --> 00:21:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've fought against the Russian army.</font>

333
00:21:44,570 --> 00:21:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're veteran guerrillas.</font>

334
00:21:47,320 --> 00:21:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This won't be a hopeless fight.</font>

335
00:21:50,030 --> 00:21:54,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we have one other advantage.</font>

336
00:21:54,890 --> 00:22:00,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, Hijikata Toshizou, have 
fought at Hakodate before.</font>

337
00:22:00,670 --> 00:22:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know exactly how to do it.</font>

338
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12" color="#62000d"><b>{\an3}<font size="17">Next Time
<font size="27">Our Kamuy</font></font></b></font>

339
00:23:35,670 --> 00:23:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next Time: Our Kamuy!</i></font>

